\pard{\pntext\f1\'B7\tab}{\*\pn\pnlvlblt\pnf1\pnindent0{\pntxtb\'B7}}\fi-360\li720\sa200\sl276\slmult1 There will be a farmon map that maps an integer ID to a farmon instance\par
{\pntext\f1\'B7\tab}When something wants to hold a reference to a farmon, it will do so by saving the key of that farmon.\par
{\pntext\f1\'B7\tab}When somethings wants to retrieve the reference, it will use the saved key to get the dictionary value (farmon instance)\par
{\pntext\f1\'B7\tab}When a farmon evolves, it will replace the value of its key with the newly evolved farmon reference to update all existing references to the old farmon.\par

