{\pntext\f1\'B7\tab}MainState - this state ticks the FarmonStateMachine and the NavigationStateMachine\par

\pard\sa200\sl276\slmult1\par
FarmonStateMachine:\par
This state machine contains the farmon's current objective:\par
States:\par

\pard{\pntext\f1\'B7\tab}{\*\pn\pnlvlblt\pnf1\pnindent0{\pntxtb\'B7}}\fi-360\li720\sa200\sl276\slmult1 IdleState - Wander around with no objective.\par
{\pntext\f1\'B7\tab}AttackState - The farmon is given a target farmon upon entering the AttackState. Move into attack range of the target farmon. If we are in attack range and the attack is not ready yet, choose random spots around the enemy to move to.\par
{\pntext\f1\'B7\tab}DefendState - The farmon is given a target location to defend up entering the DefendState. The farmon moves to the defend location and waits. If an enemy farmon enters a certain radius around the target location (taking into consideration this farmon's attack range), the defending farmon will attack the enemy farmon.\par
{\pntext\f1\'B7\tab}ProtectState - The farmon is given a target freindly farmon upon entering the ProtectState. The farmon closely follows the farmon it is protecting and if an enemy farmon enters a certain radius around the target farmon (taking into consideration this farmon's attack range),  the protecting farmon will attack the enemy farmon. If this farmon has any friendly abilities, they will prioritize the protected farmon.\par

